Package de.oth.blocklib.renderer

Class TransparentMasterRenderer

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.renderer.TransparentMasterRenderer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Renderer, DoubleBuffer
public class TransparentMasterRenderer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Renderer
The Transparent master renderer. contains a double buffered collection of objects that should be rendered this frame and the next frame.
Author:
Loher Florian
